[b]About[/b]

[color=#333333]Twenty years in financial services. Co-founded Helix Solutions in 2019 with a clear belief: that small and mid-sized businesses deserve the same quality of compliance infrastructure as the major players.

I'm proud of what we've built — a team that takes its work seriously, treats clients with integrity, and delivers results that hold up under scrutiny.

Outside of work: weekend cyclist, occasional cook, committed fan of terrible weather.[/color]

